rows.label: tlk41700151_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Have you ever ventured down to the
levels below Alba Margen?

rows.label: tlk41700151_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You can only get down there when
the Cloud Sea is low.

rows.label: tlk41700151_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Nations like Gula and Superbia
that are built on the surface of Divine Beasts
are at the mercy of the Cloud Sea level.

rows.label: tlk41700151_01_msg0004
rows.name:
That's why we tend to build our cities
on high ground, where the Cloud Sea
level doesn't have so much effect.

rows.label: tlk41700151_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Sometimes I envy nations like Avaritia
that float on the Cloud Sea, and Invidia
where they live inside the Divine Beast itself.
